PN,31701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772838680
OL,3,C'Milestone' first UK remote robotic
OL,4,Csurgery
OL,6,FThe first UK remote robotic surgery
OL,7,Fhas been hailed as a "milestone" by
OL,8,Fmedics.
OL,10,FA surgeon in London operated on a
OL,11,Fpatient with prostate cancer who was
OL,12,Fsome 2,400km away in Gibraltar.
OL,14,FThe pioneering procedure went
OL,15,F"extremely well", with patient Paul
OL,16,FBuxton reporting feeling "fantastic"
OL,17,Fjust four days after the surgery.
OL,26,@oD@VOUoD@`O]wD@AOUwD@PO]xD@ZOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772838680
OL,3,C'Milestone' first UK remote robotic
OL,4,Csurgery
OL,6,FMr Buxton, who is originally from
OL,7,FBurnham-On-Sea in Somerset but moved
OL,8,Fto Gibraltar 40 years ago, said that
OL,9,Fit was a "no-brainer" to be involved.
OL,11,FThe 62-year-old told the Press
OL,12,FAssociation that he was happy to be
OL,13,Fthe "guinea pig" patient, saying the
OL,14,Foperation has taken Gibraltar from the
OL,15,F"Championship to the Champions League"
OL,16,Fin terms of access to surgery.
OL,26,@qD@JOUqD@UO]uD@EOUuD@PO]wD@AOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772838680
OL,3,C'Milestone' first UK remote robotic
OL,4,Csurgery
OL,6,FHe was operated on by leading robotic
OL,7,Furological surgeon Professor Prokar
OL,8,FDasgupta, who told PA the surgery went
OL,9,Fto plan with a lag of only 0.06
OL,10,Fseconds between the surgical tool in
OL,11,FLondon and the robot in Gibraltar.
OL,13,FThe professor of urology said that it
OL,14,Fwas "almost as if I was there" when
OL,15,Foperating on the patient.
OL,17,FMr Dasgupta said the procedure, the
OL,18,FUK's first remote telesurgery, was a
OL,19,F"milestone".
OL,26,@vD@EOUvD@^O]{D@AOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772838680
OL,3,C'Milestone' first UK remote robotic
OL,4,Csurgery
OL,6,FThe only hospital in Gibraltar is St
OL,7,FBernard's at Europort.
OL,9,FBut residents with more complex needs
OL,10,Fwould usually travel further afield,
OL,11,Fincluding to the UK for NHS care for
OL,12,Fthose eligible.
OL,14,FAfter a shock prostate cancer
OL,15,Fdiagnosis after Christmas, Mr Buxton
OL,16,Fwas expecting to join the NHS waiting
OL,17,Flist and to travel to England for care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772838680
OL,3,C'Milestone' first UK remote robotic
OL,4,Csurgery
OL,6,FBut he was given the opportunity to be
OL,7,Fthe first patient to have the
OL,8,Ftreatment remotely and jumped at the
OL,9,Fchance.
OL,11,F"A lot of people actually said to me:
OL,12,F'You're not going to do it, are you?'"
OL,13,Fhe told PA.
OL,15,F"I thought, I'm giving something back
OL,16,Fhere.
OL,18,F"I love football ` we've literally
OL,19,Fgone from being in the Championship to
OL,20,Fthe Champions League as far as
OL,21,Fsurgeons are concerned."
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@fO]wD@AOUzD@AOU}D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772838680
OL,3,C'Milestone' first UK remote robotic
OL,4,Csurgery
OL,6,FMr Buxton, who owns a transport
OL,7,Fcompany, added: "If I hadn't gone for
OL,8,Fthe telesurgery in Gibraltar, then I
OL,9,Fwould have had to have flown to
OL,10,FLondon, I would have had to go on the
OL,11,FNHS waiting list, get the procedure
OL,12,Fdone and I would have probably been in
OL,13,FLondon for three weeks.
OL,15,F"So I thought: 'this is a no-brainer'.
OL,17,F"And it is pioneering for Gibraltar,
OL,18,Fbecause you don't need to leave
OL,19,FGibraltar.
OL,26,@oD@QOUwD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772838680
OL,3,C'Milestone' first UK remote robotic
OL,4,Csurgery
OL,6,F"Normally, any major surgeries, apart
OL,7,Ffrom minor stuff, maybe hernias and
OL,8,Fthings like that, you end up having to
OL,9,Fgo to either London or Madrid."
OL,11,FHe said he was "really well looked
OL,12,Fafter" adding: "I was feeling
OL,13,Ffantastic four days after the
OL,14,Foperation."
OL,16,F"It's been a privilege to be part of
OL,17,Fmedical history," he added.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@_O]sD@POUtD@FO]tD@POUvD@KO]xD@
OL,26,AAOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772838680
OL,3,C'Milestone' first UK remote robotic
OL,4,Csurgery
OL,6,FMr Dasgupta, who leads The London
OL,7,FClinic's Robotic Centre of Excellence,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The surgery was a milestone. It
OL,9,Fwent extremely well.
OL,11,F"We operated on an NHS patient in
OL,12,FGibraltar from The London Clinic
OL,13,F2,400km away using a robot with a 3D
OL,14,FHD camera with four arms.
OL,16,F"The robot is completely controlled
OL,17,Ffrom a console, which is like a
OL,18,Fcomputer console, using high-speed
OL,19,Flines with a time delay of, would you
OL,20,Fbelieve it, only 0.06 seconds, that 60
OL,21,Fmilliseconds."
OL,26,@pD@GOUsD@AOUxD@AOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772838680
OL,3,C'Milestone' first UK remote robotic
OL,4,Csurgery
OL,6,FA team on the ground in Gibraltar was
OL,7,Fstanding ready to take over as a
OL,8,Fprecaution in case the connection
OL,9,Fdropped.
OL,11,FThe London Clinic and Gibraltar Health
OL,12,FAuthority collaborated on the project,
OL,13,Fand the Toumai Robotic System, made by
OL,14,FMicroport, was used to perform the
OL,15,Foperation.
OL,17,FMr Dasgupta said that patients in
OL,18,Fremote areas do not always have access
OL,19,Fto the best healthcare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772838680
OL,3,C'Milestone' first UK remote robotic
OL,4,Csurgery
OL,6,FThe remote robotic surgery means that
OL,7,Fpatients can be saved the "vast
OL,8,Fexpense and inconvenience" of
OL,9,Ftravelling for care, he added.
OL,11,F"This gives us the opportunity to
OL,12,Ftreat patients in remote areas and
OL,13,Fsmaller communities by literally being
OL,14,Fable to take the best surgeon
OL,15,Fanywhere," he added.
OL,17,F"The technology now exists to provide
OL,18,Fthis benefit to patients."
OL,26,@oD@[OUpD@ZO]sD@AOUwD@JO]yD@AOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772838680
OL,3,C'Milestone' first UK remote robotic
OL,4,Csurgery
OL,6,FMr Buxton was the first of two test
OL,7,Fcases and had his procedure on
OL,8,FFebruary 11. The first "official"
OL,9,Fsurgery took place on Wednesday March
OL,10,F4.
OL,12,FOn March 4, Mr Dasgupta performed
OL,13,Fanother prostatectomy ` a surgical
OL,14,Fremoval of the prostate ` on an
OL,15,Funnamed 52-year-old man, also in
OL,16,FGibraltar.
OL,26,@pD@XOUpD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772838680
OL,3,C'Milestone' first UK remote robotic
OL,4,Csurgery
OL,6,FSpeaking after the surgery on March 4,
OL,7,FMr Dasgupta told PA: "This is a
OL,8,Fhistoric moment ` the first
OL,9,Ftelesurgery procedure from The London
OL,10,FClinic to Gibraltar, 2,400 kilometres
OL,11,Faway. Unbelievable.
OL,13,F"It went very well.
OL,15,F"We used a robot and a very
OL,16,Fspecialised connection between London
OL,17,Fto Gibraltar didn't fail at all.
OL,19,F"The time delay between the two sides
OL,20,Ffools my brain into thinking I'm in
OL,21,FGibraltar.
OL,26,@oD@VOUuD@AOUwD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772838680
OL,3,C'Milestone' first UK remote robotic
OL,4,Csurgery
OL,6,F"This is very good news for patients
OL,7,Fin Gibraltar and other remote areas."
OL,9,FHe added: "I think it is very, very
OL,10,Fexciting, the humanitarian benefit is
OL,11,Fgoing to be significant."
OL,13,FThe console in the UK was connected to
OL,14,Fthe robot in Gibraltar via fibre
OL,15,Foptics, with a backup 5G connection.
OL,17,FMr Dasgupta will perform the procedure
OL,18,Fagain on March 14, which will be live-
OL,19,Fstreamed to 20,000 world-leading
OL,20,Furological surgeons at the European
OL,21,FAssociation of Urology congress.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@eO]qD@KOUsD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772838680
OL,3,C'Milestone' first UK remote robotic
OL,4,Csurgery
OL,6,FAl Russell, chief executive at The
OL,7,FLondon Clinic, said: "The London
OL,8,FClinic is proud to be part of medical
OL,9,Fhistory and we have a strong
OL,10,Freputation for medical firsts.
OL,12,F"We hope more patients will be able to
OL,13,Fbenefit from this incredible medical
OL,14,Fbreakthrough."
OL,16,FGibraltar minister for health, Gemma
OL,17,FArias-Vasquez, added: "This is a
OL,18,Flandmark moment for the Gibraltar
OL,19,FHealth Authority and for our patients.
OL,26,@oD@VOUtD@AOUvD@NO]yD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772838680
OL,3,C'Milestone' first UK remote robotic
OL,4,Csurgery
OL,6,F"To deliver a complex procedure in
OL,7,FGibraltar with the operating surgeon
OL,8,Fbased in London shows how technology,
OL,9,Finvestment and the expertise of our
OL,10,Fclinicians are transforming
OL,11,Fhealthcare."
OL,13,FThe surgery was supported global
OL,14,Ftechnology services provider, Presidio.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/15
